Package: RefineGeo
Type: Package
Title: Facilitate address standardization and intelligent selection of geocoding coordinates
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Lucas João P. T. T.", email = "pedrottlucas@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: João P. T. T. Lucas <pedrottlucas@gmail.com>
Description: RefineGeo is an R package designed to streamline address standardization and intelligent selection of geocoding coordinates. 
    It enhances data accuracy and precision in location-based analyses by providing robust tools for refining addresses and selecting optimal coordinates based on a proprietary methodology.
